I was gonna write a note.

155
00:07:34,204 --> 00:07:37,332
Listen, someone might see us
out here.

156
00:07:37,332 --> 00:07:38,833
We can talk in that cave.

157
00:07:38,833 --> 00:07:40,168
Wha--

158
