No, you don't have to carry me!

159
00:07:42,337 --> 00:07:43,088
[Gasps]

160
00:07:43,171 --> 00:07:44,839
Uhh!

161
00:07:44,839 --> 00:07:46,216
KARA:
What is that?

162
00:07:46,341 --> 00:07:48,593
It's a foolproof way outta here.

163
00:07:48,677 --> 00:07:50,470
But why?
We're safe here.

164
00:07:50,595 --> 00:07:53,181
We have no freedom, Kara!

165
00:07:53,223 --> 00:07:54,975
I want to see what's out there.

166
00:07:55,100 --> 00:07:57,227
