217
00:10:16,241 --> 00:10:18,368
Aah! Kara, no!

218
00:10:18,409 --> 00:10:20,370
Stop! Ow!

219
00:10:21,663 --> 00:10:24,249
- Initiate grabbing.
- Ah!

220
00:10:24,290 --> 00:10:25,792
