221
00:10:25,875 --> 00:10:27,752
No! Stop it!

222
00:10:27,794 --> 00:10:30,505
Don't! No!

223
00:10:30,547 --> 00:10:33,007
[Crying] Why?

224
00:10:33,049 --> 00:10:35,426
Oh, Kara, why?

225
00:10:35,510 --> 00:10:38,012
No. [Sobbing] Why?

226
00:10:38,054 --> 00:10:40,515
DR. GROSS:
That's enough, X3-7-7.

227
00:10:40,557 --> 00:10:42,308
Let's go home.

228
00:10:42,308 --> 00:10:45,311
[Humming Founders song]

229
00:10:50,316 --> 00:10:52,026
JAKE:
I'm pretty sure she's awake.

230
00:10:52,068 --> 00:10:54,696
She's got that "focused stank"
about her.

231
00:10:56,030 --> 00:10:58,074
Susan, are you okay?

232
00:10:58,158 --> 00:10:59,701
Kara.

233
00:11:00,451 --> 00:11:02,537
My name is Kara.

234
00:11:02,579 --> 00:11:04,831
[Wind Whistling]

235
00:11:19,220 --> 00:11:21,181
This party is so crazy!

